flowchart TD
    FILE[Raw file content] --> FP1

    FP1["FP-1  Code fence stripping
    Replace content inside backtick blocks
    with blank lines before analysis
    ~60% reduction"]

    FP1 --> FP2

    FP2["FP-2  Preceding-line context
    Penalise if line above trigger contains
    never / bad example / do not
    ~15% reduction"]

    FP2 --> FP3

    FP3["FP-3  Confidence scoring
    Table rows, headings, docs/ paths
    lower the confidence score
    ~10% reduction"]

    FP3 --> FP4

    FP4["FP-4  Meta-analyzer
    One LLM call reviews findings
    with confidence 0.35 to 0.80
    Returns real / false_positive / needs_review
    ~7% reduction"]

    FP4 --> FP5

    FP5["FP-5  File-type profiles
    docs/ files require 0.85 confidence
    skill files require 0.60 confidence
    ~3% reduction"]

    FP5 --> SPLIT{Confidence
    threshold
    passed?}

    SPLIT -->|Yes| REAL["Real finding
    Reported to output"]
    SPLIT -->|No| FP["False positive
    Moved to
    suppressed_findings"]

    style FP1 fill:#1a3a2a,color:#fff,stroke:#2a5a3a
    style FP2 fill:#1a3a2a,color:#fff,stroke:#2a5a3a
    style FP3 fill:#1a3a2a,color:#fff,stroke:#2a5a3a
    style FP4 fill:#1a3a4a,color:#fff,stroke:#2a4a6a
    style FP5 fill:#1a3a2a,color:#fff,stroke:#2a5a3a
    style REAL fill:#1a4a1a,color:#fff
    style FP fill:#4a1a1a,color:#fff
